<?xml version='1.0' encoding='utf-8'?>

<activity xml:id="act-encontrarFraccionesEquivalentes" xmlns:xi="http://www.w3.org/2001/XInclude"> 

<title>[@@@@@@@@@]</title>

<statement>
  <p>[@@@@@@@@@]</p>
</statement>

<solution>
    <p>[+++++++++++++++]</p>
    <p>Sample responses:</p>
<ol>
      <li><m>\frac{1}{2}</m> is equivalent to <m>\frac{3}{6}</m> because they are the same size.</li>
      <li><m>\frac{2}{3}</m> is equivalent to <m>\frac{4}{6}</m> because they are the same size.</li>
      <li><m>\frac{6}{6}</m> is equivalent to <m>\frac{4}{4}</m> because they are both made with the whole strip.</li>
      <li><m>\frac{3}{4}</m> is equivalent to <m>\frac{6}{8}</m> because they are the same size.</li>
    </ol>
  </solution>


